   - Reads RGB values from the sensor and normalizes them to a range of [0, 1].
   - Fills the input tensor with normalized color values.
   - Invokes the interpreter to run inference.
   - Processes the output tensor to determine the predicted class label.
   - Outputs the predicted class label via serial communication using Unicode emojis.

